"title": "9313: resurrection, spiritual",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9313",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The gospel brings new life to men and women, who lived in death and darkness until they came to faith. The NT emphasis upon “being made alive in Christ” is closely linked to the resurrection of Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>Being made alive in Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:1\">EPH 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:6\">EPH 2:4–2:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:1-Ezek37:14\">EZK 37:1–37:14</a></p>\n<h2>Crossing over from death to life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24-John5:26\">JHN 5:24–5:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:3-Rom6:5\">ROM 6:3–6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:17\">1CO 15:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:13\">COL 2:13</a></p>\n<h2>Believers continue to live by the power of the risen Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:13\">PHP 4:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:17\">2CO 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:20\">GAL 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:10\">PHP 3:10</a></p>\n<h2>Results of being made alive in Christ</h2>\n<h3>Spiritual desires</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:1-Col3:2\">COL 3:1–3:2</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Spiritual assurance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:3-Col3:4\">COL 3:3–3:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24\">JHN 5:24</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual appetite</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:1-1Pet2:3\">1PE 2:1–2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:3\">JHN 3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:6\">JHN 3:6</a></p>\n<h3>Commitment to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:13\">ROM 6:13</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Love for fellow believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:14\">1JN 3:14</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Spiritual character</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:4\">ROM 7:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22-Gal5:23\">GAL 5:22–5:23</a></p>",
